title: Liliana of the Dark Realms
text: +1: Search your library for a Swamp card, reveal it, and put it into your hand. Then shuffle your library.−3: Target creature gets +X/+X or -X/-X until end of turn, where X is the number of Swamps you control.−6: You get an emblem with "Swamps you control have ‘: Add  to your mana pool.'"
